---
title: Old Cuban
tags: cocktails
---

In a #cocktail shaker{}, muddle @fresh mint leaves{6} with @simple syrup{1%oz} and @fresh lime juice{3/4%oz}. Add @aged rum{1.5%oz} and @Angostura bitters{2%dashes} along with ice. Shake until well-chilled.

Double-strain into a #coupe glass{}. Top with @chilled Champagne{2%oz} and garnish with a mint sprig.
